msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"<b>We ding this product as it is unclear if all users, regardless of which privacy laws they live under, have the same rights to have their data deleted. Sony's Playstation privacy documentation "
"seems to be contradictory on this point.</b><br/><br/> <b>Privacy Policy</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"\"We may retain information about you as long as it is necessary for us to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. In addition, we may retain your information for an additional period as is "
"permitted or required to, among other things, comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce agreements. <b>Where required by applicable law, we shall delete your information when "
"the information is no longer necessary or requested to do so.</b> Even if we delete your information from active databases, the information may remain on backup or archival media as well as other "
"information systems.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"\"Your Rights<br/>In addition to the rights described below, you can also access, amend or delete some information through your Account Settings page.<br/> Request to Access and Correct: You have "
"the right to request that we inform you of the PI we hold about you, as well as to request the correction of any inaccurate information about you.<br/> Right of Access: You have the right to request"
" that we inform you of the PI we have collected, used and shared about you, and to obtain a copy of it.<br/> <b>Right of Deletion: You have the right to request that we delete the PI we have "
"collected or retained about you in some circumstances as defined by law.</b> To request removal of certain of your PI from a blog, forum, or message board, please contact us as described in the "
"Contact Us section above. Following your request for deletion, please be aware that the information that we collect about you may still be retained for legal, accounting, business continuity "
"(backup), anti-fraud and community reasons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"In some cases, your choices to provide, change or delete information may affect our ability to deliver our Services, or your user experience. <b>We may decline to process requests which are not "
"otherwise required by applicable law.</b> You have the right not to be unlawfully discriminated against because you have exercised these rights."
msgstr ""
"Em alguns casos, suas escolhas para fornecer, alterar ou excluir informações podem afetar nossa capacidade de fornecer nossos serviços ou sua experiência de usuário. <b>Podemos recusar o "
"processamento de solicitações que não sejam exigidas de outra forma pela lei aplicável.</b> Você tem o direito de não ser discriminado ilegalmente porque exerceu esses direitos."

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid ""
"To make a Request to Access or Deletion, please visit <a id=\"a1\">www.playstation.com/ccpa</a>, or contact Consumer Services toll-free at 1-800-345-7669. After you submit a request, we will require"
" you to confirm your request, and verify your identity by requesting details of your account, devices, payment instruments or past transactions. We reserve the right to deny your requests if we "
"cannot verify your identity.\""
msgstr ""
"Para fazer uma solicitação de acesso ou exclusão, acesse <a id=\"a1\">www.playstation.com/ccpa</a> ou entre em contato com o atendimento ao consumidor gratuitamente pelo telefone 1-800-345-7669. "
"Depois de enviar uma solicitação, exigiremos que você confirme sua solicitação e verifique sua identidade solicitando dados da sua conta, dispositivos, instrumentos de pagamento ou transações "
"anteriores. Reservamo-nos o direito de negar as suas solicitações se não conseguirmos verificar a sua identidade.\""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid "Online Safety, Account Security, and Privacy Page"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "how_can_you_control_your_data"
msgid "\"We give all users the ability to access and delete the personal information we have about them. Depending on your country, you may have additional rights.\""
